problem2

Class Ranks

  • java.lang.Object
    • problem2.Ranks
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Rank

    public class Ranks
extends java.lang.Object
implements Rank
    Defines a list of rank names and rank symbols. Returns the rank names and rank symbols. The user has the flexibility of setting Ace or King as the highest rank. I have set Ace as the highest rank card. So the order of the ranks will be: 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, jack, queen, king, ace in increasing order.
    Author:
    meghna
